      "side": 1,
      "message": "I believe that it should always be an error, but this is definitely negotiable. The only reason I say it should be an error is that the current behavior is failure on duplication anyways later on in the label creation phase (https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id\u003d901411).",
